data.description:
Located in Isabella Village this neighborhood is uniquely positioned to give residents access to a luxurious resort style living! Featuring a Water Park and it's own 50+ clubhouse. The 55+ Active Adult Community of Savannah, attention is focused on the details. Tray ceilings, arched entry ways, tile floors and wood blinds. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a large study there is some flexibility in the floor plan. The primary bedroom has a spa like bath, walk in closet featuring extra shelves and hanging. The covered back patio was extended 4 feet and a walking path on the side was installed for convenience.
The HOA monthly dues includes maintenance of the front and side yard.
